Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船里有Vajra的幼虫吗?\N{\fs6}\N{\r}怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你竟然在策划政变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，这么一来你就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，稍微晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特，我要说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要传达… 我的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:45.71,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－是好还是坏，我也不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－很好啊，应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想怀着喜欢一个人的心情而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美好的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又想唱歌了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说过了吧，我已经放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露·诺姆已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再说谎了，雪露!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能抛弃歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的话\N{\fs6}\N{\r}你的歌就不可能传达给那么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是曾经站在舞台上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的感情与谎言还是分得清的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎样，米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的恋情又在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，好想死了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二形态的Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:54.06,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－为什么会出现在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不太清楚，开车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说太晚了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:16.24,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－很遗憾，婚约要取消了，凯西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我才想这么说呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是结束的报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我，三岛君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现问题了，我现在马上回来\N{\fs6}\N{\r}你待在那里别动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾啊，三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FE00&}－站住\N{\fs6}\N{\r}{\r}－站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:09.64,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－去唱歌吧，用你的歌让它们老实下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了保护这城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.85,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特，我果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我唱不出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.18,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－兰花?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这样我唱不了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌… 这种事\N{\fs6}\N{\r}我不是用来和Vajra战斗的道具！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事… 讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来，我知道唱歌需要感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你是职业歌手啊\N{\fs6}\N{\r}去做能做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声有这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我如何期盼都无法得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了，兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:10.02,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－兰花！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－等一下，七濑小姐，现在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛… 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.59,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－攻击激烈起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情等级，-7.3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能，怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊，这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是11年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:37.80,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(225,420)}这是你搞的鬼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(437,420)}不，虽然考虑过可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(296,460)}但这对我来说也是预料之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说这样行吗? 总统好像还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:49.53,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－如果比较难办的话，我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－用不着，我自己能够解决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场混乱是上天的安排，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:01.83,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－岛内出现Vajra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是的，司令部发来了紧急返航命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经甩掉它们了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,De-fold反应?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.17,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－米歇尔，卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:22.45,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－大家，没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－啊，但为什么会出现这么多Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是在岛内繁殖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:33.58,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－这种大小，枪还能起点作用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－但是，这种数量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之，先去S.M.S的基地吧\N{\fs6}\N{\r}到了那里就有武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，只不过是状态不太好罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花的歌是大家的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为功率不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了S.M.S的基地，那里有卡纳莉亚小姐的\N{\fs6}\N{\r}K{\fs25\fnArial}Ö{\r}nig (Monster) 上拆下来的Fold Wave增幅器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用了那个的话，一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.02,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－七濑小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.25,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－别害怕，这就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.43,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－赶快去终止这混乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.14,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特的手好热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:50.55,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，之前好像也被人这么牵过手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.91,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的手，也非常的热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内部的Vajra叫来了援军吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.50,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－别让它们接近船团!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akizuki被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了，Vajra接近船团!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Antares-1，外面的攻击也来了\N{\fs6}\N{\r}你去解决那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier现在就被毁掉会很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra绝对不会加害Little Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想变成强制模式的话\N{\fs6}\N{\r}就服从命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和兰花的联络呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:56.82,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－您没事吗，阁下?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－啊，是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府职能全部转移到了Battle Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后在那里进行指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢，阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就全部交给我\N{\fs6}\N{\r}雷昂·三岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼，为什么… 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗也好，死也好\N{\fs6}\N{\r}有当兵的来就足够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:33.42,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－为什么，为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－冷静下来，你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这种时候才要冷静\N{\fs6}\N{\r}知道了吗，米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡，能够使用的武器有哪些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照资料上显示\N{\fs6}\N{\r}有简化型EX-Gear和几种Valkyrie用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:52.98,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－但只靠这些对付它们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不，很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯兰，你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到Battle Frontier竟然有这种地下通道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是只有政府要员和\N{\fs6}\N{\r}总统以及家人才知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(182,460)}阿尔特，等再干掉两三只后\N{\fs6}\N{\r}就一口气冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.64,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(392,460)}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯兰，准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:45.36,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－呐，米歇尔，能给我刚才的答案吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的恋情又在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行踪不明，现在寻找中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有这种东西，连我自己都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，你果然是个胆小鬼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你，米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你… 这种时候… 说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，就是这种时候才要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了，米歇尔\N{\fs6}\N{\r}好好记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔特，你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕死的话，还怎么恋爱啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FE00&}好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:55.14,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－阿尔特，掩护柯兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.02,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－抓紧了，兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花·李怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩一唱歌Vajra不是就会停止吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}明明说已经逃脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:22.67,liner notes,,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得把话说得太好听了\N{\fs6}\N{\r}政府的那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了，我们全都要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(231,420)}我们都会死么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:40.00,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(394,420)}没关系的，艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:40.00,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,460)}妈妈他们一定… 一定会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 我好怕啊，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭，就算有危险\N{\fs6}\N{\r}爸爸也会拿性命来保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用生命做交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.16,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能抛弃歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:06.47,Default italize,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的话\N{\fs6}\N{\r}你的歌就不可能传达给那么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得还能传达吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰花，如果你是\N{\fs6}\N{\r}希望的歌姬的话，那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在绝望中歌唱给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:50.17,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－救助还没来吗，军队呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－有谁啊? 快来做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银河的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fold Wave增幅器没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了，要多加小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐，阿尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正喜欢上什么人的话\N{\fs6}\N{\r}是要拼上性命的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.29,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.69,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6464FF&}－米歇尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.05,Default conflict green,,0000,0000,0000,,－骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这臭虫!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊，柯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在，都没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(263,460)}我也… 我也…\N{\fs6}\N{\r}对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以抚平的创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,折磨着人们的心灵\N{\fs6}\N{\r}引导向诀别的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回  苍色晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.65,0:24:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲恋的歌声在银河回响
